  <name>Vapad</name>
  <summary>Edits text and stays out of the way</summary>
	<description>
	  <p>
	    Vapad is a gtk4 text editor with a simple interface that
      enables the most commonly used comfort features by default.
      It strives, above all, to stay out of the user's way.
	  </p>
	  <p>Features:</p>
	  <ul>
	    <li>Syntax highlighting for all languages supported by GtkSourceView</li>
	    <li>
	      Comfortfeatures like line numbers, long line marker and auto-indent on
	      by default
	    </li>
	    <li>Tabbed interface</li>
	    <li>Light and dark themes using LibAdwaita</li>
	    <li>Themeable syntax highlighting</li>
	    <li>Quick search bar</li>
	    <li>Advanced search including replace all in document, session or selection</li>
	    <li>Standard keyboard shortcuts for all major interactions</li>
	    <li>Simple and light interface with no preferences window</li>
	  </ul>
	</description>
